ices or of potential new services that may be offered.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Pepeelika.com does not sell, rent or lease its customer\r\nlists to third parties. Pepeelika.com may, from time to time, contact you on\r\nbehalf of external business partners about a particular offering that may be of\r\ninterest to you. In those cases, your unique personally identifiable\r\ninformation (e-mail, name, address, telephone number) is not transferred to the\r\nthird party. In addition, Pepeelika.com may share data with trusted partners to\r\nhelp us perform statistical analysis, send you email or postal mail, provide\r\ncustomer support, or arrange for deliveries. All such third parties are\r\nprohibited from using your personal information except to provide these\r\nservices to Pepeelika.com, and they are required to maintain the\r\nconfidentiality of your information.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Pepeelika.com does not use or disclose sensitive personal\r\ninformation, such as race, religion, or political affiliations, without your\r\nexplicit consent.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Pepeelika.com keeps track of the Web sites and pages our\r\ncustomers visit within Pepeelika.com, in order to determine what Pepeelika.com\r\nservices are the most popular. This data is used to deliver customized content\r\nand advertising within Pepeelika.com to customers whose behavior indicates that\r\nthey are interested in a particular subject area.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Pepeelika.com Web sites will disclose your personal\r\ninformation, without notice, only if required to do so by law or in the good\r\nfaith belief that such action is necessary to: (a) conform to the edicts of the\r\nlaw or comply with legal process served on Pepeelika.com or the site; (b)\r\nprotect and defend the rights or property of Pepeelika.com; and, (c) act under\r\nexigent circumstances to protect the personal safety of users of Pepeelika.com,\r\nor the public.</p>','General','General