ers. He adds, ÃƒÆ’Ã‚Â¢ÃƒÂ¢Ã¢â‚¬Å¡Ã‚Â¬Ãƒâ€¦Ã¢â‚¬Å“Borders also function as a\r\nheight lengthening element in the design and gives a break from the monotony of\r\nextra long flounce and flare.ÃƒÆ’Ã‚Â¢ÃƒÂ¢Ã¢â‚¬Å¡Ã‚Â¬Ãƒâ€šÃ‚Â</span><br>\r\n<br>\r\n</span><b><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\ncolor:#666666\">Things to keep in mind while choosing an anarkali border</span></b><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;line-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#666666\"><br>\r\n<span style=\"background:white\">The border you choose can make or break a design\r\nas it can overpower and kill the look if you go wrong with it. Things like\r\nlength, fabric and design of the anarkali play an important role while choosing\r\nthe right border for your outfit.</span><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<span style=\"background:white\">Aniket says, ÃƒÆ’Ã‚Â¢ÃƒÂ¢Ã¢â‚¬Å¡Ã‚Â¬Ãƒâ€¦Ã¢â‚¬Å“Maintaining the rhythmic balance\r\nof an outfit is an essential factor. Calf length</span></span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\n&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#666666\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\"><a href=\"http://idiva.com/topic/anarkalis\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-size:\r\n10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\ncolor:#FF3333;text-decoration:none;text-underline:none\">anarkalis</span></a></span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;line-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#666666;background:white\">should\r\nbe finished with simple mirco borders. For floor length anarkalis, dress it up\r\nusing different borders which are eight to 10 inches broad.ÃƒÆ’Ã‚Â¢ÃƒÂ¢Ã¢â‚¬Å¡Ã‚Â¬Ãƒâ€šÃ‚Â</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\n&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#666666\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;line-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#666666\"><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<span style=\"background:white\">ÃƒÆ’Ã‚Â¢ÃƒÂ¢Ã¢â‚¬Å¡Ã‚Â¬Ãƒâ€¦Ã¢â‚¬Å“If your anarkali&acute;s flare starts from the\r\nshoulder, you can opt for a heavy border,ÃƒÆ’Ã‚Â¢ÃƒÂ¢Ã¢â‚¬Å¡Ã‚Â¬Ãƒâ€šÃ‚Â says Aditi.</span><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<span style=\"background:white\">Designer Pawan Sachdeva explains how to use\r\nborders on different fabrics and colours. He says, ÃƒÆ’Ã‚Â¢ÃƒÂ¢Ã¢â‚¬Å¡Ã‚Â¬Ãƒâ€¦Ã¢â‚¬Å“If the fabric of your\r\nanarkali is very delicate (such as chiffon), then stay away from heavily\r\nembroidered borders.ÃƒÆ’Ã‚Â¢ÃƒÂ¢Ã¢â‚¬Å¡Ã‚Â¬Ãƒâ€šÃ‚Â He adds, ÃƒÆ’Ã‚Â¢ÃƒÂ¢Ã¢â‚¬Å¡Ã‚Â¬Ãƒâ€¦Ã¢â‚¬Å“If your outfit has too much work on it, opt for\r\nthin and delicate borders. Lastly, if the colour of the suit is too jazzy and\r\nvibrant, use a border that is subtle and vice versa.ÃƒÆ’Ã‚Â¢ÃƒÂ¢Ã¢â‚¬Å¡Ã‚Â¬Ãƒâ€šÃ‚Â</span></span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\n&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#666666\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;line-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#666666\"><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<span style=\"background:white\">ÃƒÆ’Ã‚Â¢ÃƒÂ¢Ã¢â‚¬Å¡Ã‚Â¬Ãƒâ€¦Ã¢â‚¬Å“Strictly avoid bordering uneven or asymmetrical\r\nhems,ÃƒÆ’Ã‚Â¢ÃƒÂ¢Ã¢â‚¬Å¡Ã‚Â¬Ãƒâ€šÃ‚Â adds Aniket.</span><br>\r\n<br>\r\n</span><b><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\ncolor:#666666\">Borders according to your body type</span></b><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;line-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#666666\"><br>\r\n<span style=\"background:white\">Just like there are different patterns of</span></span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\n&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#666666\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\"><a href=\"http://idiva.com/topic/anarkalis\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-size:\r\n10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\ncolor:#FF3333;text-decoration:none;text-underline:none\">anarkalis</span></a></span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\n&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#666666\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;line-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#666666;background:white\">for\r\ndifferent body types, one border doesn&acute;t work for all. Aniket tells us what\r\nborder you should choose for your body type -</span><span style=\"font-size:\r\n10.5pt;line-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#666666\"><br>\r\n<br>\r\n</span><b><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\ncolor:#666666\">Petite</span></b><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;line-height:115%;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\ncolor:#666666;background:white\">: Women with a petite frame should sport bright\r\nand sleek styles. Avoid bold and broad anarkali borders as they will overpower\r\nthe entire look. Pretty and dainty patterns, delicate cutwork and feminine\r\ntextures work best for the petite body type.</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;\r\nline-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\ncolor:#666666\"><br>\r\n<br>\r\n</span><b><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\ncolor:#666666\">Tall</span></b><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;line-height:115%;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\ncolor:#666666;background:white\">: Tall women are blessed as this is the best\r\nbody type to sport an anarkali. A tall frame permits you to experiment with\r\nbold and broad borders. You can also fabric block and colour block your\r\nanarkali with interesting borders using graphic geometrics and bright Indian\r\npatterns such as gota, Kutch work and bright brocades.</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;line-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#666666\"><br>\r\n<br>\r\n</span><b><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\ncolor:#666666\">Slim</span></b><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;line-height:115%;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\ncolor:#666666;background:white\">: If your body type is slim, avoid anything too\r\nfragile and delicate. Borders used in gradation and geometric pattern work well\r\nfor this body type. Use similar borders on your sleeves as well.</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;line-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#666666\"><br>\r\n<br>\r\n</span><b><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\ncolor:#666666\">Plump</span></b><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;line-height:115%;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\ncolor:#666666;background:white\">:</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#666666\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\"><a href=\"http://idiva.com/topic/anarkalis\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-size:\r\n10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\ncolor:#FF3333;text-decoration:none;text-underline:none\">Anarkalis</span></a></span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\n&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#666666\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;line-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#666666;background:white\">are\r\nnot a good option for women who are plump. But, if you still want to wear them,\r\nexperiment with asymmetrical hems and uneven flare as it add lightness to the\r\ndesign. Avoid under bust cut and opt for the shoulder panel variety.</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;line-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#666666\"><br>\r\n<b><span style=\"border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;\r\npadding:0in;background:white\"><br>\r\n</span></b></span><b><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;\r\nline-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\ncolor:#666666\">Trends in anarkali border designs</span></b><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;line-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#666666\"><br>\r\n<span style=\"background:white\">ÃƒÆ’Ã‚Â¢ÃƒÂ¢Ã¢â‚¬Å¡Ã‚Â¬Ãƒâ€¦Ã¢â‚¬Å“Traditional South Indian karvat style woven\r\nvarieties are quite haute this seasonÃƒÆ’Ã‚Â¢ÃƒÂ¢Ã¢â‚¬Å¡Ã‚Â¬Ãƒâ€šÃ‚Â, says Aniket. Authentic Paithani and\r\nKarnataki temple borders also look great. Rose gold and copper finished borders\r\nare trendy this season, more than the regular gold and silver. ÃƒÆ’Ã‚Â¢ÃƒÂ¢Ã¢â‚¬Å¡Ã‚Â¬Ãƒâ€¦Ã¢â‚¬Å“Borders in neon\r\nand bright colours such as orange, red, green, gold and silver with zari\r\nembroidery, kundan work and thread work are quite a hit this season,ÃƒÆ’Ã‚Â¢ÃƒÂ¢Ã¢â‚¬Å¡Ã‚Â¬Ãƒâ€šÃ‚Â concludes\r\nSachdeva.</span><br>\r\n<br>\r\n</span><b><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\ncolor:#666666\">What to avoid</span></b><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;\r\nline-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\ncolor:#666666\"><br>\r\n<span style=\"background:white\">You can sometimes go terribly wrong with\r\nborders. Hence, it&acute;s important that you avoid making certain mistakes. Holani\r\nsays, ÃƒÆ’Ã‚Â¢ÃƒÂ¢Ã¢â‚¬Å¡Ã‚Â¬Ãƒâ€¦Ã¢â‚¬Å“You need to keep in mind your body type before picking borders. Shorter\r\nframes should never opt for over-the-top or broad borders.ÃƒÆ’Ã‚Â¢ÃƒÂ¢Ã¢â‚¬Å¡Ã‚Â¬Ãƒâ€šÃ‚Â Borders can\r\nhorizontally break the outfit into lengths and make one look shorter and\r\nlarger. Aniket says, ÃƒÆ’Ã‚Â¢ÃƒÂ¢Ã¢â‚¬Å¡Ã‚Â¬Ãƒâ€¦Ã¢â‚¬Å“Play with textures of the same tonal colour family and\r\ndon&acute;t be afraid to mix gold with silver, black with brown and shine with matt.ÃƒÆ’Ã‚Â¢ÃƒÂ¢Ã¢â‚¬Å¡Ã‚Â¬Ãƒâ€šÃ‚Â\r\nÃƒÆ’Ã‚Â¢ÃƒÂ¢Ã¢â‚¬Å¡Ã‚Â¬Ãƒâ€¦Ã¢â‚¬Å“Avoid pairing extremely contrasting colour borders with your suit,ÃƒÆ’Ã‚Â¢ÃƒÂ¢Ã¢â‚¬Å¡Ã‚Â¬Ãƒâ€šÃ‚Â says\r\nSachdeva.</span><br>\r\n<br>\r\n</span><i><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\ncolor:#666666\">Image courtesy: Viral Bhayani, BCCL</span></i></p>','General','General','','Same','Active','2013-12-11 10:24:53','smallCONT-00149Life Style-02 anarkali_borders1.jpg','midCONT-00149Life Style-02 anarkali_borders1.jpg','bigCONT-00149Life Style-02 anarkali_borders1.jpg','USR-000001','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',4),('CONT-00150',NULL,'How to Save: On Your Beauty Regimen','','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:6.0pt;mso-line-height-alt:13.2pt;\r\nmso-outline-level:1;background:white;vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"line-height: 13.65pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">If you haven&acute;t noticed already, your salon has most likely\r\nrevised their menu and hiked their rates