gn:baseline\"><b><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;\r\nline-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\ncolor:#666666\">Schedule opportune salon visits</span></b><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">:\r\nDon&acute;t visit the parlour the moment you notice some</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: &acute;Times New Roman&acute;, serif;\"><a href=\"http://idiva.com/topic/hair\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;\r\nline-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;color:#FF3333;text-decoration:\r\nnone;text-underline:none\">hair</span></a></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">sprout\r\non your knee. Time your parlour visits according to your party calendar or just\r\nin time for some weekend revelry. This way you will save money on the extra\r\nparlour visit. Plus, a few extra days of pants and long-sleeved shirts won&acute;t\r\nhurt, now would they?</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\ncolor:#666666\">Primp with tweezers</span></b><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;\r\nline-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\ncolor:#666666;background:white\">: Make a pair of tweezers your best friend.\r\nThey work well for those un